# 🤰 PregManage — Product Requirements Document (PRD)

> **Project**: Pregnancy Management System  
> **Version**: v0.1 (Draft)  
> **Date**: March 2, 2026  
> **Status**: 🟡 Awaiting User Review  

---

## 1. Overview

**PregManage** is a web-based pregnancy management system designed for Anganwadi centers. It enables **Anganwadi workers** to register pregnant women, track their health status through periodic questionnaires, and manage patient records — all under the supervision of an **Admin**.

---

## 2. Users & Roles

| Role | Count | Description |
|------|-------|-------------|
| **Admin** | 1+ | Superuser who manages the system — creates/manages Anganwadi worker accounts. Full system access. |
| **Anganwadi Worker** | 25 | Field workers who register patients, conduct health questionnaires, and manage their assigned patients. |
| **Patient (Pregnant Woman)** | Many | End beneficiaries — do NOT have login access. Their data is entered by Anganwadi workers. |

---

## 3. Authentication System

### 3.1 Admin Authentication
- Separate login page/portal for Admin
- Admin credentials (details TBD — to be discussed later)
- Admin can:
  - Create Anganwadi worker accounts (username + password)
  - Manage (edit/delete) worker accounts
  - *(More admin capabilities to be added later)*

### 3.2 Anganwadi Worker Authentication
- Dedicated login page for Anganwadi workers
- Each of the 25 workers has unique credentials (created by Admin)
- Upon successful login → redirected to the **Patient Selection Screen**

---

## 4. Application Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Landing Page] --> B{Select Role}
    B -->|Admin| C[Admin Login]
    B -->|Anganwadi Worker| D[Worker Login]
    
    C --> E[Admin Dashboard]
    E --> F[Create/Manage Workers]
    
    D --> G[Patient Selection Screen]
    G --> H{New or Existing Patient?}
    
    H -->|New Patient| I[Patient Registration Form]
    I --> J[Upload / Capture Photo]
    J --> K[Save Registration]
    K --> L[Pregnancy Questionnaire]
    
    H -->|Existing Patient| M[Search / Select Patient]
    M --> L
    
    L --> N[Submit Questionnaire]
    N --> O[Confirmation / Summary]
```

---

## 5. Screens & Features

### 5.1 🔐 Landing / Login Page
- Clean, professional landing page
- Two distinct entry points:
  - **Admin Login** button/card
  - **Anganwadi Worker Login** button/card
- Each redirects to its respective login form

### 5.2 🔑 Admin Login Page
- Username & Password fields
- Login button
- Error handling for invalid credentials
- *(Admin dashboard features to be detailed later)*

### 5.3 🔑 Anganwadi Worker Login Page
- Username & Password fields
- Login button
- Error handling for invalid credentials
- On success → redirect to **Patient Selection Screen**

### 5.4 📋 Patient Selection Screen (Post Worker Login)
After a worker logs in, they see a screen with two clear options:

| Option | Action |
|--------|--------|
| **Register New Patient** | Opens the patient registration form |
| **Already Registered Patient** | Opens a search/select screen to find existing patient, then redirects to questionnaire |

### 5.5 📝 New Patient Registration Form
Collects personal information / bio data of the pregnant woman:

| Field | Type | Required |
|-------|------|----------|
| Full Name | Text | ✅ |
| Age | Number | ✅ |
| Husband's Name | Text | ✅ |
| Phone Number | Tel | ✅ |
| Address | Textarea | ✅ |
| Aadhaar Number | Text | ✅ |
| LMP (Last Menstrual Period) Date | Date | ✅ |
| Expected Delivery Date (EDD) | Date (auto-calculated or manual) | ✅ |
| Blood Group | Dropdown | ✅ |
| Gravida (No. of pregnancies) | Number | ✅ |
| Para (No. of deliveries) | Number | ✅ |
| **Photo** | Upload file / Capture via camera | ✅ |

> [!NOTE]
> The fields above are a suggested set based on standard Anganwadi records. Please review and let me know if any fields should be added, removed, or modified.

**After successful registration → auto-redirect to Pregnancy Questionnaire**

### 5.6 📸 Photo Upload / Capture
- Two options for the patient photo:
  - **Upload**: Select an image file from device
  - **Capture**: Open device camera and take a photo directly
- Preview of the photo before saving
- Photo is stored and associated with the patient record

### 5.7 ❓ Pregnancy Health Questionnaire
A simple **Yes/No** questionnaire with **10 questions** related to pregnancy health. Displayed after registration (new patient) or after selecting an existing patient.

| # | Question | Response |
|---|----------|----------|
| 1 | Are you experiencing any bleeding or spotting? | Yes / No |
| 2 | Do you have severe headaches or blurred vision? | Yes / No |
| 3 | Are you experiencing swelling in hands, feet, or face? | Yes / No |
| 4 | Do you have persistent nausea or vomiting? | Yes / No |
| 5 | Are you feeling reduced or no fetal movement? | Yes / No |
| 6 | Do you have any abdominal pain or cramping? | Yes / No |
| 7 | Are you experiencing fever or chills? | Yes / No |
| 8 | Do you have difficulty breathing or chest pain? | Yes / No |
| 9 | Have you been taking your iron/folic acid supplements regularly? | Yes / No |
| 10 | Have you attended your last scheduled antenatal checkup? | Yes / No |

> [!NOTE]
> These are suggested pregnancy-related questions. Please review and modify as needed. Questions can be customized to match your specific Anganwadi program requirements.

- Each question has a **Yes** and **No** toggle/button
- Submit button at the bottom
- On submit → show confirmation/summary page

### 5.8 ✅ Confirmation / Summary Page
- Shows a summary of the submitted questionnaire
- Indicates any "red flag" answers (e.g., bleeding, reduced fetal movement)
- Option to go back to patient selection or log out

