## 6. Tech Stack (Proposed)

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| **Frontend** | HTML, CSS, JavaScript (Vanilla — premium, modern UI) |
| **Backend** | Node.js with Express.js |
| **Database** | MongoDB (or SQLite for simpler setup) |
| **Authentication** | Session-based or JWT |
| **Photo Storage** | Local filesystem or cloud (e.g., Cloudinary) |
| **Deployment** | TBD |

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Please confirm your preferred tech stack. If you have any preferences (e.g., React, Python/Flask, MySQL, Firebase, etc.), let me know and I'll adjust accordingly.

