## 7. Data Model (High-Level)

```mermaid
erDiagram
    ADMIN {
        string id PK
        string username
        string password_hash
        string role
    }
    
    ANGANWADI_WORKER {
        string id PK
        string name
        string username
        string password_hash
        string created_by FK
        datetime created_at
    }
    
    PATIENT {
        string id PK
        string full_name
        int age
        string husband_name
        string phone
        string address
        string aadhaar
        date lmp_date
        date edd
        string blood_group
        int gravida
        int para
        string photo_url
        string worker_id FK
        datetime registered_at
    }
    
    QUESTIONNAIRE {
        string id PK
        string patient_id FK
        string worker_id FK
        boolean q1_bleeding
        boolean q2_headache
        boolean q3_swelling
        boolean q4_nausea
        boolean q5_fetal_movement
        boolean q6_abdominal_pain
        boolean q7_fever
        boolean q8_breathing
        boolean q9_supplements
        boolean q10_checkup
        datetime submitted_at
    }
    
    ADMIN ||--o{ ANGANWADI_WORKER : creates
    ANGANWADI_WORKER ||--o{ PATIENT : registers
    PATIENT ||--o{ QUESTIONNAIRE : has
    ANGANWADI_WORKER ||--o{ QUESTIONNAIRE : submits
```

